<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 03:15:12 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>星展银行首席执行官表示，特朗普将对削减交易持开放态度，这可能适合中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/dbs-ceo-says-trump-will-be-open-cutting-deals-which-could-suit-china-2024-07-09/</link><description>新加坡星展银行集团首席执行官皮尤什·古普塔(Piyush Gupta)周二表示，美国总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普(Donald Trump)如果获胜，将愿意达成交易，这可能适合中国。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 02:43:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/dbs-ceo-says-trump-will-be-open-cutting-deals-which-could-suit-china-2024-07-09/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市跟随华尔街走高，市场希望鲍威尔采取鸽派立场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-09/</link><description>亚洲股市周二跟随华尔街走高，因市场希望美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔在当天晚些时候对宽松前景发表鸽派言论，而美元则稳定在四周低点附近。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 02:15:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-09/</guid></item><item><title>中金公司高管看到中国客户在越南的战略机遇</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/cicc-executive-sees-strategic-opportunities-chinese-clients-vietnam-2024-07-09/</link><description>中国国际金融公司东南亚业务负责人兼新加坡首席执行官吴志强周二表示，该行在越南看到了中国企业客户更多的战略机遇。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 02:08:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/cicc-executive-sees-strategic-opportunities-chinese-clients-vietnam-2024-07-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国和白俄罗斯在波兰边境附近开始联合军演</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-belarus-start-joint-military-drills-near-polish-border-2024-07-09/</link><description>白俄罗斯和中国国防部表示，中国和白俄罗斯周一开始联合军事演习，演习在距离北约成员国波兰边境仅几英里的地方举行，并在北约峰会前夕拉开帷幕。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 01:55:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-belarus-start-joint-military-drills-near-polish-border-2024-07-09/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国的兴趣，澳大利亚承诺为太平洋银行业提供更多资金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-pledges-more-funds-pacific-banking-amid-china-interest-2024-07-09/</link><description>澳大利亚周二承诺增加对太平洋岛国的投资，以支持其银行系统，此前全球金融公司以风险为由限制了对太平洋岛国的服务，而中国正寻求增加其在该地区的影响力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 01:47:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-pledges-more-funds-pacific-banking-amid-china-interest-2024-07-09/</guid></item><item><title>鲍威尔作证前美元下跌；欧元抵御法国的不确定性</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-droops-before-powell-testimony-euro-weathers-france-uncertainty-2024-07-09/</link><description>周二，美元兑主要货币汇率徘徊在多周低点附近，仍因周五意外疲软的就业报告而受到影响，交易员等待美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔(Jerome Powell)的证词，以获取有关利率走势的线索。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 01:38:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-droops-before-powell-testimony-euro-weathers-france-uncertainty-2024-07-09/</guid></item><item><title>斯里兰卡即将结束债务重组谈判，寻求平衡印度和中国关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/sri-lanka-take-few-more-weeks-wrap-up-debt-restructuring-talks-2024-07-09/</link><description>斯里兰卡外交部长阿里·萨布里周二表示，斯里兰卡将在几周内结束与国际债券持有人就重组进程进行的谈判，这是该岛国摆脱数十年来最严重金融危机的重要一步。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 01:30:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/sri-lanka-take-few-more-weeks-wrap-up-debt-restructuring-talks-2024-07-09/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾驳回中国对南海环境破坏的指控</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-rejects-chinas-accusation-environmental-damage-south-china-sea-2024-07-09/</link><description>周二，菲律宾否认了中国关于其在有争议的仁爱礁搁浅的军舰破坏了该地区珊瑚礁生态系统的指控，并将破坏海洋环境的责任归咎于北京。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 01:13:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-rejects-chinas-accusation-environmental-damage-south-china-sea-2024-07-09/</guid></item><item><title>微软将向中国员工提供苹果设备，理由是缺乏Android服务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/microsoft-offer-apple-devices-employees-china-cites-absence-android-services-2024-07-08/</link><description>微软发言人周一表示，该公司打算向其在中国的员工提供基于苹果 iOS 的设备来访问身份验证应用程序，理由是该国没有谷歌的 Android 服务。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 20:38:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/microsoft-offer-apple-devices-employees-china-cites-absence-android-services-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪将斥资10亿美元在土耳其建设工厂</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-ev-maker-byd-build-1-bln-plant-turkey-2024-07-08/</link><description>土耳其工业和技术部长周一表示，中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪有限公司已与土耳其政府达成协议，将在土耳其建设一座价值 10 亿美元的生产工厂，年产能为 15 万辆汽车。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 15:44:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-ev-maker-byd-build-1-bln-plant-turkey-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国山东省计划到2025年锂电池产业规模达140亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-shandong-province-plans-14-bln-lithium-battery-industry-by-2025-2024-07-08/</link><description>周一，当地政府通知显示，中国山东省计划到明年发展价值 1000 亿元人民币（138 亿美元）的锂电池产业。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 11:14:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-shandong-province-plans-14-bln-lithium-battery-industry-by-2025-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国官方媒体猛烈抨击中储粮涉嫌使用油轮运输食用油</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-state-media-slams-sinograin-over-alleged-use-fuel-tankers-transport-2024-07-08/</link><description>中国官方媒体周一批评国家粮食储备公司中储粮，此前当地媒体报道称，该公司的油轮也被用来运输食用油，引发食品安全担忧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 10:56:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-state-media-slams-sinograin-over-alleged-use-fuel-tankers-transport-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>德国商报报道，ASML 首席执行官表示世界需要中国生产的传统芯片</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-ceo-says-world-needs-legacy-chips-china-is-producing-handelsblatt-reports-2024-07-08/</link><description>设备制造商ASML首席执行官在周一发表的德国商报采访中表示，包括德国汽车行业在内的芯片买家需要中国芯片制造商目前正在投资的老一代计算机芯片。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 10:08:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-ceo-says-world-needs-legacy-chips-china-is-producing-handelsblatt-reports-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯官员称美国离开武器条约是为了制造武器威胁中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russian-official-says-us-left-arms-treaty-build-weapons-menace-china-2024-07-08/</link><description>俄罗斯副外长谢尔盖·里亚布科夫周一指责美国决定退出苏联时代的军控条约，以便华盛顿可以开始制造武器来恐吓中国。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 10:01:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russian-official-says-us-left-arms-treaty-build-weapons-menace-china-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国称菲律宾军舰“损坏”南海环礁珊瑚礁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-claims-philippine-warships-damaged-reef-atoll-south-china-sea-2024-07-08/</link><description>中国周一表示，菲律宾军舰在南海南沙群岛“非法”搁浅，“严重破坏”了该地区的珊瑚礁生态系统，两国在这片广阔水道的环礁上存在争议领土。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 09:53:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-claims-philippine-warships-damaged-reef-atoll-south-china-sea-2024-07-08/</guid></item></channel></rss>